content:
Good Morning Everyone,
I've been making a few changes to my page,The cover is temporary.....trying to update and simplify. I wish I could do that with my life! lol! So, I've been working on this Story involving a safe company in New Jersey. Yesterday, One of the alleged  new owners freaked out on me! I thought I was gonna have to drop this guy,  fortunately it never degenerated to that. This company is on everyone's radar! selling safes, taking the money and not delivering the product. They've also been linked to a multi-million dollar jewelry heist! There's a lot going on here! I wish I could tell you more, but I have to wait, the situation is fluid. I should have another story on this ready in a  little less than two weeks. 
On Monday I'm going to help out a family from Selden, L.I. Their son was hit by a car 4 years ago. He sustained Traumatic brain inuries. He can't walk or talk. His parents payed a stem cell transplant surgeon 10-thousand dollars for an transplant proceedure, now the Dr won't give the family the documents for their insurance! That's Monday at 10PM on PIX 11 NEWS. 

Have a good weekend everyone!

Howard
